tafsir[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"Halkiima juuɗe bappa nelaaɗo -yo o his- Abii laha biy Abdul Muttalibi e pertude golle makko, sabu ko loratno nelaaɗo, golle mum cooyi."
  111,2,"Hol ko jawdi mum nafi mbo? ndi ittanaani mbo lepte, ndi addanaani mbo yurmeende."
  111,3,"Ma o naat nyande darnga yiite nge lewlewndu, o tampa e nguleeki henge."
  111,4,"Ma debbo makko Ummu jamiil naat yiite sabu ko o loratno nelaaɗo-yo o his-weddaade gi*e e laawol makko."
  111,5,"Ina e daande makko ɓoggol moccangol haa tiiɗi o ɗowree ngol faade yiite."
